        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-[family-name:var(--font-heading)] mb-6">5. NISS Scoring</h2>
        <div class="prose mb-8">
          <p>
            The Neural Impact Scoring System (NISS) is a purpose-built vulnerability scoring system for neural devices. In contrast to CVSS, which measures confidentiality, integrity, and availability, NISS quantifies five dimensions specifically relevant to brain-computer interfaces:
          </p>
