            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
              Quantifies physical damage to neural tissue. Scores range from None (N) through Low, High, to Critical (C), denoting permanent tissue destruction. A buffer overflow scores BI:N, whereas a seizure-inducing technique scores BI:H or BI:C.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#f59e0b]"></span>
              <h4 class="font-semibold font-[family-name:var(--font-heading)] text-sm">Cognitive Integrity (CG)</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
              Assesses impact on a victim's thought processes, perception, and decision-making. A phantom sensory injection scores CG:H, while neural data eavesdropping with no cognitive effect scores CG:N. A technique that alters the subject's sense of agency scores CG:C.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#8b5cf6]"></span>
